# workingSet

**Type Property**

The persistent identifier representing the working set of documents and directories.

## Declaration

```swift
static let workingSet: NSFileProviderItemIdentifier
```

## Discussion

For more information about the working set, see  [doc://com.apple.fileprovider/documentation/FileProvider/defining-your-file-provider-s-content#Create-the-Working-Set-and-Enumerate-its-Content].

## Constants

- **rootContainer**: The persistent identifier for the root directory of the file provider’s shared file hierarchy.
- **trashContainer**: The persistent identifier for the parent of all trashed items.
